* The force majeure clause only gets you so far: I haven=E2=80=99t been onl=
ine as much this past week, prioritizing friends and family as many people =
around me scramble to figure out where to go for the next few weeks, months=
, and even years. However, I=E2=80=99ve felt a tremendous amount of d=C3=A9=
j=C3=A0
vu back to the early days of Covid, regarding what small businesses, and re=
tailers of every size, are now facing=E2=80=94store closures, loss of merch=
andise, fulfillment breakdowns, challenges with employees being able to mak=
